	elp: Thanks to the donors of\n\nThe Seattle Public Library Foundation\n\nf
	or sponsoring this event.\n\nEvent Logistics:\n\n\, Registration is not re
	quired but these programs are very popular and the room capacity can fill 
	up quickly.\, While Homework Help is available to students from kindergart
