	r fees)\n\nComa Cinema:\n\nComa Cinema is the longest running project of s
	ongwriter and producer\, Mathew Lee Cothran\, known for his work as Elvis 
	Depressedly and The Goin’ Nowheres. Coma Cinema has been active since 2005
	\, remaining independent and happily obscure in an ever dulling world. Com
	a Cinema is committed to fighting entropy by the alchemy of art\, bringing
	 thoughts to life in Cothran and his listener’s minds with a spirit of dee
	p gratitude for those who have listened to and shared his music for many y
